command.text: M82 ; Set absolute mode for extruder
; M206 X-5 Y-5 Z-5 ; Need to add offset of 5 mm as we retract 5 mm from home position
; M400 ; Wait for the queue to be empty before answering OK
G28 X0 Y0 Z0 ; Home all axes
M400 ; Wait for the queue to be empty before answering OK
G92 X0 Y0 Z-9.8 E0 ; Reset machine coordinates to zero
M400 ; Wait for the queue to be empty before answering OK
G0 Z0 ; Move head to middle position
; G0 {X:X%.4f} {Y:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:E%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move (MOVE_TO_COMMAND)
G0 {BacklashOffsetX:X%.4f} {BacklashOffsetY:Y%.4f} {Z:Z%.4f} {Rotation:E%.4f} F{FeedRate:%.0f} ; Send standard Gcode move (MOVE_TO_COMMAND) with Backlash compensation
M400 ; Wait for moves to complete before returning
M800 ; Turn off down camera LED
M802 ; Turn off up camera LED
M801 ; turn on down camera light
M803 ; turn on bottom camera light
M802 ; turn off bottom camera light
M812 ; Turn off nozzle 1 vacuum solenoid
M810 ; Turn off nozzle 2 vacuum solenoid
M813 ; Turn on nozzle 1 vacuum solenoid
M811 ; Turn on nozzle 2 vacuum solenoid
M812 ; Turn off nozzle 1 vacuum solenoid
M810 ; Turn off nozzle 2 vacuum solenoid
